      "text": "ここ最近、瑠依ちゃんの様子が変なんや\n上の空っちゅうか、心ここにあらずっちゅうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui has been acting strange lately.\nShe seems absent-minded… like her heart isn’t in it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.9333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
